### 📁 utils/
Reusable helper functions and classes.

- `preprocessing.py`: Standardization, segmentation
- `data_loader.py`: Batching and formatting for training
- `metrics.py`: Custom MAE, MAPE, RMSE calculations
- `plot_utils.py`: Training loss & accuracy visualization

```python
# metrics.py
def mean_absolute_error(y_true, y_pred):
    return np.mean(np.abs(y_true - y_pred))
